FR1.1 System will store user, customer, and books in a database(M)

FR2.1 Allow user to view monthly and yearly sale reports based on market demand, and past and current data(S)

FR3.1 Allows user to set an inventory threshold that alerts user user of low stock(M)

FR3.2 Allows user to categorize database alphabetically and by genre, author, keyword, and ISBN(M)

